com.palantir.ptoss.cinch.example.simple
Class OnChangeExample

java.lang.Object
  com.palantir.ptoss.cinch.example.simple.OnChangeExample

public class OnChangeExample
extends java.lang.Object

Simple example illustrating use of OnChange. Fires a method call on an Change event. Note that for a component like JToggleButton, this includes every mouse event, such that a toggle will generate six ChangeEvents.

See Also:
ChangeListener - contains a list of components that support ChangeListeners.
